        public WSResponse(String url,
                  int status,
                  String statusName,
                  String statusDescription,
                  String contentType,
                  Long size,
                  InputStream bodyStream)
        Creates a new Pipeline2WSResponse with the given HTTP status code, status name, status description and content body.
        Parameters:
        url - the URL
        status - the HTTP status
        statusName - the HTTP status name
        statusDescription - the HTTP status description
        contentType - the content type
        size - the size of the body
        bodyStream - the body as a InputStream
